Welcome to Kirrirom National Park
This place is very good place for people who really love to live with nature and enjoy life with the nature sound such as wind sound,rain sound, bird singing
For accomodation, we have Vkirrirom resort which provides a comfortable zone to spend your holiday with your family,your relatives and your special person 
It has many types of rooms such as pipe house,tent,luxury tent,cottage or small villa and bungalow
Can you imagine it like having modern restaurant on the mountain? However,we have a pine restuarant.
The restaurant is around by tall pine trees which you can enjoy the good view while you are having meal.
It is a different restaurant from the restaurant in the city.
